Subject: Re: [T2] Hard starting when hot

Just a thought, but check your fuel line.  If it is close enough to engine 
to get hot after the engine stops you might be getting the equivalent of 
vapor lock in the gas line, making it harder to get fuel to the fuel pump 
and carb.

Cheers,

John

